alt_text:
A digital art, one page comic; arranged in the style of a moodboard with a short narrative. The themes revolve around death and substance abuse. The main color theme is blue and white. Each panel has symbolism that relate to flowers or butterflies. Burning books reveal sudden change as a bullet casing falls from the pages with smoke. 

The panels contain;
An ivy wrapped hand holds up a skull with a bullet hole, surrounded by cobwebs, butterflies, and tree branches. A small, withering bouquet with a blue hydrangea is tied with a blue ribbon. A poppy flower lays next to an overflowing bottle of wine and a dying butterfly. A blue hand with blue veins lays outstretched with poisonous flowers growing from the skin; in this hand is a dead butterfly. A man is looking over his shoulder, holding a bouquet of flowers to hide his scarred visage. The bouquet prominently features white lilies and other small flowers.

